    <h1>New Prod&#xAD;ucts Sony a7s III MIR&#xAD;ROR&#xAD;LESS CAM&#xAD;ERA</h1>
    <h2></h2>
    <section>
        <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/textview" title="The Straits Times">The Straits Times</a>
        - <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/20200916/textview" title="The Straits Times - 2020-09-16"><time>2020-09-16</time></a>
